# SmileSchool - CSS Styling Project

## Project Description
A responsive landing page for SmileSchool, implementing advanced CSS techniques based on a Figma design. Focuses on proper styling, layout, and responsiveness.

## Key Features
- **Professional header** with navigation
- **Hero section** with call-to-action
- **Instructor profiles** with achievements
- **Video testimonial** section
- **Tutorial cards** with star ratings
- **Membership benefits** grid
- **FAQ accordion** section
- **Footer** with social links

## Technical Requirements
✔ Pure HTML/CSS (no frameworks)  
✔ W3C validated code  
✔ Responsive design  
✔ Proper image optimization  
✔ External CSS only (no inline styles)  

